            "id": 6010572,
            "title": "致伸受台幣升值影響5月營收持平 AIoT產品出貨動能穩健",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電腦周邊廠致伸 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4915:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4915\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4915-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公告 48.4 億元，約與上月持平；累計前 5 月營收 244.3 億元，較去年同期成長 2.7%；致伸表示，部分客人因應關稅影響提前拉貨，加上 AIoT 產品出貨動能穩健，然而<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>大幅升值，對<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">台幣</a>營收表現略有影響。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010572%2Fl%2Fdb719e8f31056b890ac61caae7b3cbad.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">致伸5月營收受台幣升值影響 AIoT產品出貨動能穩健。(圖：致伸提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>致伸 5 月營收 48.4 億元，月增 0.4%、年減 5.3%；累計前 5 月營收 244.3 億元，較去年同期成長 2.7%</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>致伸提到，將持續深化多感合一感測融合（X-IN-1 Sensory Fusion）技術，拓展視聽覺科技（Audiovisual Technology）領域的創新應用，積極推動 Edge AI 在公共安全（Public Safety）與 AIoT（B2B）視覺解決方案、AI 視訊會議及車載產品等領域，擴大智慧感測技術的應用版圖。同時，B2B 專案需求穩定，特別是在 AI 智慧監控領域有不錯的表現。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>致伸表示，將密切關注關稅及市場變化，正加速泰國廠產能擴建，預期年底產能占比將提升至近 30%，並持續投資自動化設備提高生產效率，滿足客戶多元化需求。此外，公司亦積極深耕工業視覺、聲學檢測與 AI 智慧監控等具高成長潛力的利基市場，強化高附加價值產品組合，為未來營運注入成長動能。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
